      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;heading-element&#34; id=&#34;三五五伤寒热少厥微指头寒默默不欲食烦躁数日小便利色白者此热除也欲得食其病为愈若多而呕胸胁烦满者其后必便血&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;三五五：「伤寒」，热少，厥微，指头寒，默默不欲食，烦躁，数日小便利色白者，此热除也；欲得食，其病为愈；若多而呕，胸胁烦满者，其后必便血。&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a href=&#34;#%e4%b8%89%e4%ba%94%e4%ba%94%e4%bc%a4%e5%af%92%e7%83%ad%e5%b0%91%e5%8e%a5%e5%be%ae%e6%8c%87%e5%a4%b4%e5%af%92%e9%bb%98%e9%bb%98%e4%b8%8d%e6%ac%b2%e9%a3%9f%e7%83%a6%e8%ba%81%e6%95%b0%e6%97%a5%e5%b0%8f%e4%be%bf%e5%88%a9%e8%89%b2%e7%99%bd%e8%80%85%e6%ad%a4%e7%83%ad%e9%99%a4%e4%b9%9f%e6%ac%b2%e5%be%97%e9%a3%9f%e5%85%b6%e7%97%85%e4%b8%ba%e6%84%88%e8%8b%a5%e5%a4%9a%e8%80%8c%e5%91%95%e8%83%b8%e8%83%81%e7%83%a6%e6%bb%a1%e8%80%85%e5%85%b6%e5%90%8e%e5%bf%85%e4%be%bf%e8%a1%80&#34; class=&#34;heading-mark&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;svg class=&#34;octicon octicon-link&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 16 16&#34; version=&#34;1.1&#34; width=&#34;16&#34; height=&#34;16&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;</description>
