    <item>
      <title>辨厥阴病脉证并治法：三四六</title>
      <link>https://acuherb.xyz/posts/shanghanlun-346/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Jun 2025 10:55:56 +0800</pubDate><author>124768092@qq.com (AcuHerb)</author>
